cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IT

This paper deals with learning transformation-invariant representations of image data, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves optimization and machine learning techniques, which are also relevant to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of dictionaries and optimization schemes, which are relevant to the sub-category of information theory (cs.IT).
